---
import ph from '../assets/light-bulb/placeholder.svg';
import lightBulb from '../assets/light-bulb/light-bulb.png';
import img1 from '../assets/light-bulb/img1.jpeg';
import img2 from '../assets/light-bulb/img2.jpeg';

const shell =
	"min-h-dvh bg-white dark:bg-zinc-950 font-[system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe_UI','Helvetica_Neue',Arial,sans-serif] text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50 **:box-border";
const eyebrow = 'text-[0.6875rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500';
---

<div class={shell}>
	<header class="border-b border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white/90 dark:bg-zinc-950/90 backdrop-blur-sm">
		<div
			class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-4"
		>
			<a
				href="/product-design"
				class="text-sm text-zinc-500 transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:text-zinc-50"
			>
				← Product design
			</a>
			<p class={`m-0 text-right ${eyebrow}`}>1.6 Light bulb recycle</p>
		</div>
	</header>

	<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-12 pb-10 sm:pt-16 sm:pb-12">
		<p class={`m-0 ${eyebrow}`}>1.6 Light bulb recycle</p>
		<h1 class="m-0 mt-2 text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
			Light Bulb Recycle
		</h1>
		<hr class="mt-6 max-w-2xl border-0 border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800" />
	</section>

	<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-20 sm:pb-24">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
			<div>
				<p class={`m-0 ${eyebrow}`}>Project brief</p>
				<div class="mt-5 space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
					<p>Design a small lamp and use the light bulb as a diffuser.</p>
					<p>
						A broken light bulb doesn’t have to become waste. I had a broken bulb with a plastic
						diffuser, so I designed a small lamp that repurposes that diffuser as the light cover.
					</p>
					<p>
						I came up with this design family. Each light uses a 3 V coin cell, an LED filament, and
						a TTP223 capacitive touch sensor.
					</p>
					<p>
						My personal favourite is the one on the right. The lamp turns on when you lift it up and
						set it back down on the table.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="flex min-w-0 flex-col gap-6 lg:sticky lg:top-6">
				<figure
					class="m-0 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800/70 shadow-sm"
				>
					<img
						src={lightBulb.src}
						width={1200}
						height={900}
						alt="Three lamp variants: white spherical diffusers on black, red, and blue printed bases"
						class="h-auto w-full object-cover"
						loading="eager"
						decoding="async"
					/>
					<figcaption class="border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-950 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
						Design family — shared diffuser, different base forms and colours.
					</figcaption>
				</figure>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
					<figure
						class="m-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800/70 shadow-sm"
					>
						<img
							src={img1.src}
							width={600}
							height={800}
							alt="Top view into orange base: coin cell, green TTP223 board, and glowing LED filament"
							class="aspect-[3/4] h-auto w-full object-cover"
							loading="lazy"
							decoding="async"
						/>
						<figcaption class="border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-950 px-3 py-2.5 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
							Internals — cell, touch sensor, filament.
						</figcaption>
					</figure>
					<figure
						class="m-0 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800/70 shadow-sm"
					>
						<img
							src={img2.src}
							width={600}
							height={800}
							alt="Finished orange-base lamp with diffuser, warm glow on a grey surface"
							class="aspect-[3/4] h-auto w-full object-cover"
							loading="lazy"
							decoding="async"
						/>
						<figcaption class="border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-950 px-3 py-2.5 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
							Prototype assembled and lit.
						</figcaption>
					</figure>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer class="border-t border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-950">
		<div
			class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-10 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400"
		>
			<span>Bora Tavman — Light bulb recycle</span>
			<a
				href="/product-design"
				class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-50 underline decoration-zinc-300 dark:decoration-zinc-600 underline-offset-4 transition-colors hover:decoration-zinc-900 dark:hover:decoration-zinc-300"
			>
				Back to contents
			</a>
		</div>
	</footer>
</div>
